---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  pageType="guide"
  guideTopic="cost"
  title="What Does a Shipping Container Cost? Pricing Factors | Steel Box Direct"
  description="Understand what affects shipping container pricing. Size, condition, location, delivery, and market factors explained."
>
  <div class="guide-header" style="background: var(--c4-cost); color: var(--cream);">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="sh" style="border-color: var(--cream);">
        <span class="idx">§ 04</span>
        <span class="nm" style="color: var(--cream);">Decision: Cost</span>
        <span class="tg" style="color: var(--cream);">Market Analysis</span>
      </div>
      <h1 class="big" style="color: var(--cream);">What will it<br><em>Really cost?</em></h1>
      <p class="guide-lede" style="opacity: .9;">
        All-in. Container, delivery, setup. No surprise fees. Container pricing is regional and fluctuates
        with the shipping market—we'll show you the drivers.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="guide-content">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="row">
        <div class="main-col">
          <h2>The Four Price Drivers</h2>
          <p>Instead of guessing, evaluate your quotes using these four standard drivers of container cost.</p>

          <div class="driver-card" style="border-left-color: var(--c4-cost);">
            <h3>1. Size</h3>
            <div class="m" style="color: var(--c4-cost); margin-bottom: 12px;">Predictable base</div>
            <p>Larger units cost more total, but less per square foot. A 40-foot unit provides 2x the space of a 20-foot for only ~40-60% more cost.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="driver-card" style="border-left-color: var(--c2-cond);">
            <h3>2. Condition</h3>
            <div class="m" style="color: var(--c2-cond); margin-bottom: 12px;">The biggest variance</div>
            <p>Condition determines 50% of the price spread. A "Cargo Worthy" used unit is the sweet spot for most agricultural and equipment storage.</p>
            <div class="who" style="background: var(--c2-cond); color: var(--cream);">→ 50% savings vs new</div>
          </div>

          <div class="driver-card" style="border-left-color: var(--c3-deliver);">
            <h3>3. Logistics</h3>
            <div class="m" style="color: var(--c3-deliver); margin-bottom: 12px;">Delivery distance</div>
            <p>Delivery is often 15-25% of the total project. Within 100 miles of Cincinnati is our primary tier. Complex sites requiring cranes add to the labor cost.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="driver-card" style="border-left-color: var(--yellow);">
            <h3>4. Market Cycles</h3>
            <div class="m" style="color: var(--yellow-d); margin-bottom: 12px;">The timing factor</div>
            <p>Prices fluctuate monthly based on global shipping volume and regional inventory. Patience usually equals savings.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <aside class="sidebar-col">
          <div class="authority-card">
            <div class="m">Pricing Insights</div>
            <ul>
              <li><strong>Cincinnati</strong> pricing is 15% lower than coastal markets.</li>
              <li><strong>Logistics labor</strong> is 20% of the total quote.</li>
              <li><strong>Used units</strong> provide equivalent weather protection for 50% less.</li>
            </ul>
          </div>

          <div class="cta-card">
            <h4>Get your real number</h4>
            <p>We provide all-in, delivered quotes. No hidden fees.</p>
            <a href="/quote/" class="btn">Request a Quote <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M5 12h14M13 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
          </div>
        </aside>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .guide-header {
      padding: 80px 0 64px;
      border-bottom: 2.5px solid var(--ink);
    }
    .guide-lede {
      font-size: 22px;
      line-height: 1.45;
      margin: 40px 0 0;
      max-width: 720px;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .guide-content {
      padding: 96px 0;
      background: var(--cream);
    }

    .row {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1.5fr 1fr;
      gap: 80px;
      align-items: start;
    }

    .driver-card {
      background: white;
      border: 2px solid var(--ink);
      border-left: 8px solid var(--ink);
      padding: 32px;
      margin-top: 40px;
      box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 var(--ink);
    }
    .driver-card h3 {
      font-family: var(--narrow);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 28px;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
    }
    .who {
      font-family: var(--mono);
      font-size: 10px;
      letter-spacing: .08em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      padding: 4px 8px;
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--cream);
      display: inline-block;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }

    .authority-card {
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--cream);
      padding: 32px;
      border: 2px solid var(--ink);
    }
    .authority-card .m { color: var(--yellow); margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .authority-card ul { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
    .authority-card li { margin-bottom: 16px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.45; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(246,241,231,.1); padding-bottom: 16px; }
    .authority-card li:last-child { border: none; }

    .cta-card {
      margin-top: 40px;
      background: white;
      border: 2px solid var(--ink);
      padding: 32px;
      box-shadow: 8px 8px 0 var(--c4-cost);
    }
    .cta-card h4 { font-family: var(--narrow); font-size: 24px; text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; }
    .cta-card p { font-size: 15px; margin-bottom: 20px; }

    @media (max-width: 960px) {
      .row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 48px; }
      .guide-header { padding: 48px 0; }
      .big { font-size: clamp(48px, 10vw, 80px); }
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>